&lt;li&gt;Adhere to HIPAA and company policies and procedures to ensure data security and regulatory compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and apply superior knowledge of changes and updates to coding guidelines, reimbursement trends, and health payment policy language.&lt;/li&gt;
