&lt;li&gt;Possess the CCS (Certified Coding Specialist) or CPC (Certified Professional Coder) credentials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superior knowledge of HCPCS, CPT, ICD-10-CM/PCS coding, and US healthcare payment methodologies for Commercial, Marketplace, Medicare, and Medicaid.&lt;/li&gt;
